Type: Package
Package: quartohelp
Title: Chat Interface to Quarto Documentation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Tomasz", "Kalinowski", , "tomasz@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Launches an interactive chat app that retrieves and
    summarizes relevant Quarto documentation using both semantic and
    keyword-based search via an OpenAI-powered assistant. Returns
    authoritative excerpts, includes links to official resources, and
    helps users accomplish specific Quarto tasks quickly.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
